-- China Industrial Companies’ Profit Falls 1.3% in First Quarter
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-04-27T01:33:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-27/china-industrial-companies-profit-falls-1-3-in-first-quarter.html
Chinese industrial companies’
profit dropped 1.3 percent in the first quarter from a year
earlier, the National Bureau of Statistics said on its website
today.  Net income dropped 5.2 percent in the first two months of
2012, the bureau said in March.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Scott Lanman at 
